Since logistic regression is the simplest model here, let's take a look at coefficients from this model.

<sklearn.metrics._plot.confusion_matrix.ConfusionMatrixDisplay at 0x7fdeef4dbb38>

AUC on test set is better than mean cross-validated AUC, so we can assume that model was not overfitted. The biggest challenge for the model was to properly classify rainy days, probably beacue of the class imbalance. Other metrics such as F1 score or recall might be useful in further development of the best model.
